<h1>Make a Decision</h1>
<p>Making a group decision with Decisive Team is a 3 step process:</p>
<%= form_with(model: [@decision]) do |form| %>
  <h2>1. Ask a question</h2>
  <p>Type the question that this decision will answer.</p>
  <div>
    <%= form.text_field :question, placeholder: 'Question' %>
  </div> 
  <h2>2. Gather options</h2>
  <p>
    <%= form.select :options_open, options_for_select([['Everyone', true], ['Just you', false]], selected: 'Everyone') %>
    will be able to add options on the decision page.
  </p>
  <h2>3. Make a decision</h2>
  <p>
    <%= form.number_field :duration, value: 24, style: 'width:48px;' %>
    <%= form.select :duration_unit, options_for_select(['minute(s)','hour(s)', 'day(s)', 'week(s)'], selected: 'hour(s)') %>
    will be given for everyone to vote.
  </p>
  <hr style="height:1px;" />
  <p>Go to the decision page and share the link with your team.</p>
  <%= form.submit 'Go to decision page' %>
<% end %>
